OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FA man from West Sussex suffering from
OL,7,F"grandiose delusions" who stalked an
OL,8,FInstagram travel influencer to Bali
OL,9,Fafter threatening to kidnap her has
OL,10,Fbeen sentenced to a hospital order.
OL,12,FRob Keating, 40, of Old Crawley Road
OL,13,Fin Horsham, was convicted at
OL,14,FPortsmouth Crown Court of two offences
OL,15,Fof stalking involving fear of violence
OL,16,Fagainst US photographer and former
OL,17,Flawyer Alexandra Saper.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
