OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FPsychiatrist Daron Aslanyan told the
OL,7,Fhearing that he had diagnosed Keating
OL,8,Fas having a delusional disorder as he
OL,9,Fsuffered "grandiose delusions about
OL,10,Fbeing able to change the world which
OL,11,Fwas a contributing factor to his
OL,12,Foffending".
OL,14,FHe added: "Because he was isolated he
OL,15,Fwas looking for someone who would fit
OL,16,Fhis world view with this person being
OL,17,Fable to change the world through
OL,18,Fsocial media or otherwise."
OL,26,@qD@JOUtD@JO]vD@KOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FHe said that Keating had "no insight
OL,7,Finto him having a mental disorder" and
OL,8,Fhad "not demonstrated any empathy to
OL,9,Fthe victim".
OL,11,FJudge Michael Bowes KC told the court
OL,12,Fthe hospital order with a restriction
OL,13,Forder was required for Keating to
OL,14,Freceive treatment for his mental
OL,15,Fhealth disorder which he might refuse
OL,16,Fin a prison environment because of his
OL,17,Ffailure to accept his diagnosis.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUoD@bO]pD@EOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FHe said: "My over-riding concern is to
OL,7,Fprotect the general public, and
OL,8,FAlexandra Saper in particular, from
OL,9,Fany future harm."
OL,11,FAlexandra Bull, prosecuting, said
OL,12,FKeating first started following Ms
OL,13,FSaper, who has more than 100,000
OL,14,Ffollowers of her TheWayfaress
OL,15,FInstagram account, in June 2022 before
OL,16,Fsending her a direct message.
OL,18,FShe said that Ms Saper found the
OL,19,Fmessage from Keating as "weird and
OL,20,Fcreepy, and didn't make sense".
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@QO]{D@YOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FMs Bull said that after blocking
OL,7,FKeating, he sent her "incessant and
OL,8,Fconstant" emails and videos to her
OL,9,Fbusiness account which became
OL,10,F"increasingly intense" as well as
OL,11,F"sexual in nature, aggressive and
OL,12,Foffensive", and he was "speaking to
OL,13,Fher as if she was in a relationship
OL,14,Fwith him".
OL,16,FThe prosecutor added: "She read an
OL,17,Femail that he said he was in love with
OL,18,Fher, wanted to be with her and would
OL,19,Fdo whatever was necessary, and 'if
OL,20,Fthat involves kidnapping, so be it'."
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@IO]rD@AOUrD@VO]sD@AOUtD@JO]tD@
OL,26,AXOUvD@IO]xD@WOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
