OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FMs Bull said that Keating then told Ms
OL,7,FSaper he would give up his job to
OL,8,Ftravel to Bali to be with her and at
OL,9,Fthe end of January 2023 he had bought
OL,10,Fa plane ticket and travelled to the
OL,11,FIndonesian island.
OL,13,FShe said the defendant had sent Ms
OL,14,FSaper messages with one saying "I just
OL,15,Fwant to punish you when I see you",
OL,16,Fanother asking to have dinner with her
OL,17,Fand saying: "You are never going to
OL,18,Fget rid of me."
OL,26,@vD@`OUwD@bO]yD@MOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
