OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FMs Bull said he also sent an image of
OL,7,Fa person in a suitcase, causing Ms
OL,8,FSaper to be "very scared" and forcing
OL,9,Fher to leave her home to live with
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,FShe added: "She was terrified to have
OL,13,Fsomeone watching her every move."
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@YO]tD@LOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
