OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FDespite being arrested on his return
OL,7,Fto Gatwick airport in March 2023,
OL,8,FKeating, formerly of Havant in
OL,9,FHampshire, contacted Ms Saper again
OL,10,Fmore than a year later and sent her
OL,11,Fscreenshots of flights to Bali with
OL,12,Fthe caption "Round Two", leading to
OL,13,Fhim being arrested again in November
OL,14,F2024.
OL,16,FIn her victim impact statement read to
OL,17,Fthe court, Ms Saper that she was
OL,18,Fforced her to flee first her home and
OL,19,Fthen Bali as she started to suffer
OL,20,Fpanic attacks.
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
