OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FShe said: "My mental health crumbled,
OL,7,FI disappeared from social media, my
OL,8,Fbusiness came to a screeching halt and
OL,9,FI was completely isolated from
OL,10,Ffriends, I could barely eat or sleep."
OL,12,FMs Saper said that she had started her
OL,13,Fsocial media account to encourage
OL,14,Fwomen to travel independently but
OL,15,Fadded: "I lived and worked according
OL,16,Fto these beliefs until they were
OL,17,Fshattered by a stranger who found me
OL,18,Fonline."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@fO]wD@HOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
