FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1782154094
OL,3,CHorsham man who stalked Bali
OL,4,Cinfluencer given hospital order
OL,6,FShe added: "I hoped ignoring him would
OL,7,Fmake him stop, instead he became more
OL,8,Fobsessed, more sexually explicit and
OL,9,Fmore aggressive, then came the
OL,10,Fthreats, he said he would do whatever
OL,11,Fit took to be with me, including
OL,12,Fkidnapping."
OL,26,@nD@LOUtD@LO]
